The challenge with that is that a broad umbrella that\xe2\x80\x99s being applied all across enterprise computing, and it\xe2\x80\x99s a little bit of each person wants to make of it what they want to make of it. As we said, for example, software as a service is a big growth opportunity in cloud computing, because the end user doesn\xe2\x80\x99t know where that application sits, so it\xe2\x80\x99s amiss in the cloud and they access it through a browser, wherever they connect.
